#

Tropical Mango Juice

10 min
$3.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

TropicalAmerican

Course:

BeverageSnack

Tags:

JuiceDrinkTropicalRefreshing

Description

A refreshing and vibrant juice bursting with tropical flavors, perfect for quenching your thirst on a sunny day!

Ingredients

  • mango: 2 ripe
  • water: 1 cup
  • sugar (optional): 1-2 tablespoons
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • ice cubes: as needed
